ross the web to add to your document.\",\"leftpanel-search-empty-stock-photos\":\"Search a wide variety of <w0>stock photos</w0> across the web to add to your document.\",\"leftpanel-search-load-more\":\"Load more...\",\"leftpanel-search-no-results\":\"No search results.\",\"leftpanel-search-v2\":\"Search\",\"leftpanel-sort-ai-search-terms\":\"content,group,pair,organize,arrange,categorize,cluster,reorder\",\"leftpanel-stock-photos\":\"Stock photos\",\"leftpanel-summarize-ai-search-terms\":\"content,outline,summarization,condense,highlight,key points,summary,overview\",\"leftpanel-terraform-export\":\"Terraform export\",\"leftpanel-themes-panel-v2\":\"Themes\",\"license-request-onload-dialog-detail-comment-custom-flow\":\"You currently have comment only access. Request a Lucid Suite license via the <w0>service desk</w0> to edit, collaborate, and create your own documents.\",\"license-request-onload-dialog-detail-comment-limited\":\"Your access is limited to commenting.\",\"license-request-onload-dialog-detail-limited\":\"You currently have limited access on this account.\",\"license-request-onload-dialog-detail-limited-custom-flow\":\"You currently have limited access on this account. Request a Lucid Suite license via the <w0>service desk</w0> to edit, collaborate, and create your own documents.\",\"license-request-onload-dialog-detail-view-custom-flow\":\"You currently have view only access. Request a Lucid Suite license via the <w0>service desk</w0> to edit, collaborate, and create your own documents.\",\"license-request-onload-dialog-detail-view-limited\":\"Your access is limited to viewing.\",\"license-request-onload-dialog-headline-create-like-inviter\":\"Create documents like <w0>{inviterName}'s</w0> with full access\",\"license-request-onload-dialog-headline-create-like-inviter-trial\":\"Create documents like <w0>{inviterName}'s</w0> with instant full access.\",\"license-request-onload-dialog-headline-create-like-teammates\":\"Create documents like your teammates with full access\",\"license-request-onload-dialog-headline-create-like-teammates-trial\":\"Create documents like your teammates with instant full access.\",\"limited-access-user-chart-onboarding-stepper-get-started\":\"Get Started\",\"limited-access-user-chart-onboarding-stepper-infotext-comments\":\"Press <w0>C</w0> to leave comments and @ mention others to notify them. You can find all conversations in the Comments & Tasks panel.\",\"limited-access-user-chart-onboarding-stepper-infotext-productivity-v2\":\"From flowcharts to strategy maps, the Lucid Suite helps you plan, design, and collaborate without limits, unlock a <w0>free trial</w0> when you request a license.\",\"limited-access-user-chart-onboarding-stepper-infotext-share\":\"Click \\\"Share\\\" in the top right to invite teammates and set access. Set permissions to control who can edit and share your work.\",\"limited-access-user-chart-onboarding-stepper-infotext-what-you-can-do-d\":\"Limited Access lets you view, comment, and download. A full license unlocks flowcharts, org charts, and more. Get a <w0>free trial</w0> when you request a license.\",\"limited-access-user-chart-onboarding-stepper-next\":\"Next\",\"limited-access-user-chart-onboarding-stepper-previous\":\"Previous\",\"limited-access-user-chart-onboarding-stepper-request-license\":\"Request License\",\"limited-access-user-chart-onboarding-stepper-title-comments\":\"Add Comments\",\"limited-access-user-chart-onboarding-stepper-title-productivity\":\"Unlock More Productivity!\",\"limited-access-user-chart-onboarding-stepper-title-share\":\"Share Board\",\"limited-access-user-chart-onboarding-stepper-title-what-you-can-do\":\"What you can do in Lucidchart\",\"link-unfurl-default-document-title\":\"Document\",\"link-unfurl-folder-default-title\":\"Folder\",\"link-unfurl-invitation-default-title\":\"Document invitation\",\"link-unfurl-new-document-default-title\":\"New document\",\"link-unfurl-new-document-title\":\"New from {templateTitle}\",